a long, pleez look</span><hr size=1> Hello all! I would like to leave on this board a little bit about myself as I am looking for a guild (I have one in mind but I would really like to see if there is a guild that would fit my interests). I want to make a well-informed decision for my new home on the drinal server and I want to leave some points about my philosophy of guild structure. <br>
<br>
1. I wish to join a guild that is about completely sharing and pooling resourses for the good of the guild. I kind of shy away from guilds that have individuals that sell an item in the market when a member in the guild can clearly use the item. The reason I feel this way is because I believe whole heartedly in guild support and this includes items and money etc. There may be no guild like this but for one, I hate selling crap and secondly, that person that you've strengthened in the guild can save yer ass in a battle.<br>
<br>
2. I wish to join a guild that limits alt characters. 1 primary, and 1 secondary, if possible. I've found that guilds with people that have 3+ alts tend to &quot;water down&quot; the strength of the guild. If we &quot;keep the cream&quot; on the primary characters so to speak, the the guild evolves strongly in my opinion.<br>
<br>
3. I wish to find a guild that has mostly 35 or old higher level characters. The reason for this aint to be snobby, its so that I can be able to associate and get exp with every char in the guild, I wanna be able to hang with all of my guild mates if possible. 50+ would be better but not required.<br>
<br>
A little bit about myself, I started playing on Mith Marr as a ogre warrior named Grissil Blockhead. I led a guild called fleur de lance for a bit and I learned a lot about people and guilds during that time (plus my philosophy above, was directly derived from the mistakes that I made while I ran said guild, Vive la FDL all you old school friends). About a year and a half ago I stopped playing him and gave my account to my buddy, and he played him for a couple of levels. I bought a home during this break and just recently started playing back on drinal as he moved my account (thank god btw hehe). So, I have my account back and actually played this toon (Skarl Speedbump) up to 52. <br>
<br>
I have a 52 ogre warrior, mostly stripped, a 52 mage (primary) in pretty good equip, a 35 wizard that can gg to most places, and I'm just playing around with a little cleric on my off time.<br>
I have some recent Fear experience, and some old school (several patches ago) Hate experience, and have been in guk a LOT. hehe.<br>
<br>
I play on eastern standard time, and I do not (sorry) have a cable modem but I rarely go LD.<br>
<br>
I do have references if you would like to give me a tell in game I can direct you to my old guild leader, and guild as a whole as I think we have parted on good terms, and we are still very much good friends.<br>
<br>
Thank you of your kind consideration,<br>
<br>
please email me or send me a tell in game, thanks<br>
